{
  "thag14.1:0.1": "Verses of the Senior Monks 14.1 ",
  "thag14.1:0.2": "The Book of the Fourteens ",
  "thag14.1:0.3": "Chapter One ",
  "thag14.1:0.4": "Revata of the Acacia Wood ",
  "thag14.1:1.1": "Since I’ve gone forth ",
  "thag14.1:1.2": "from the lay life to homelessness, ",
  "thag14.1:1.3": "I’ve not been aware of any thought ",
  "thag14.1:1.4": "that is ignoble and hateful. ",
  "thag14.1:2.1": "“May these beings be killed! ",
  "thag14.1:2.2": "May they be slaughtered! May they suffer!”—",
  "thag14.1:2.3": "I’ve not been aware of any such thought ",
  "thag14.1:2.4": "in all this long while. ",
  "thag14.1:3.1": "I have been aware of loving-kindness, ",
  "thag14.1:3.2": "limitless and well-developed; ",
  "thag14.1:3.3": "gradually consolidated ",
  "thag14.1:3.4": "as it was taught by the Buddha. ",
  "thag14.1:4.1": "I’m friend and comrade to all, ",
  "thag14.1:4.2": "sympathetic for all beings! ",
  "thag14.1:4.3": "I develop a mind of love, ",
  "thag14.1:4.4": "always delighting in harmlessness. ",
  "thag14.1:5.1": "The unfaltering, the unshakable: ",
  "thag14.1:5.2": "I gladden that mind. ",
  "thag14.1:5.3": "I develop a divine meditation, ",
  "thag14.1:5.4": "which reprobates do not cultivate. ",
  "thag14.1:6.1": "When in a meditation  free of placing the mind, ",
  "thag14.1:6.2": "a disciple of the Buddha ",
  "thag14.1:6.3": "is at that moment blessed ",
  "thag14.1:6.4": "with noble silence. ",
  "thag14.1:7.1": "As a rocky mountain ",
  "thag14.1:7.2": "is unwavering and well grounded, ",
  "thag14.1:7.3": "so when delusion ends, ",
  "thag14.1:7.4": "a monk, like a mountain, doesn’t tremble. ",
  "thag14.1:8.1": "To the man who has not a blemish ",
  "thag14.1:8.2": "who is always seeking purity, ",
  "thag14.1:8.3": "even a hair-tip of evil ",
  "thag14.1:8.4": "seems as big as a stormcloud. ",
  "thag14.1:9.1": "As a frontier city ",
  "thag14.1:9.2": "is guarded inside and out, ",
  "thag14.1:9.3": "so you should ward yourselves—",
  "thag14.1:9.4": "don’t let the moment pass you by. ",
  "thag14.1:10.1": "I don’t long for death; ",
  "thag14.1:10.2": "I don’t long for life; ",
  "thag14.1:10.3": "I await my time, ",
  "thag14.1:10.4": "like a worker waiting for their wages. ",
  "thag14.1:11.1": "I don’t long for death; ",
  "thag14.1:11.2": "I don’t long for life; ",
  "thag14.1:11.3": "I await my time, ",
  "thag14.1:11.4": "aware and mindful. ",
  "thag14.1:12.1": "I’ve served the teacher ",
  "thag14.1:12.2": "and fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions. ",
  "thag14.1:12.3": "The heavy burden is laid down, ",
  "thag14.1:12.4": "the conduit to rebirth is eradicated. ",
  "thag14.1:13.1": "I’ve attained the goal ",
  "thag14.1:13.2": "for the sake of which I went forth ",
  "thag14.1:13.3": "from the lay life to homelessness—",
  "thag14.1:13.4": "the ending of all fetters. ",
  "thag14.1:14.1": "Persist with diligence: ",
  "thag14.1:14.2": "this is my instruction. ",
  "thag14.1:14.3": "Come, I’ll be fully quenched—",
  "thag14.1:14.4": "I’m liberated in every way. "
}